OL,3,CShadow minister meets farmers to
OL,4,Cdiscuss industry issues
OL,6,FA family has expressed its concerns
OL,7,Fabout changes to inheritance tax rules
OL,8,Fin a meeting with the shadow farming
OL,9,Fminister.
OL,11,FRobbie Moore MP visited the family
OL,12,Ffarm of the Bells, who have worked
OL,13,Ftheir land near Dumfries since 1922.
OL,15,FTom and Sheila Bell worry that reforms
OL,16,Fto inheritance tax will make it
OL,17,Fdifficult for their son, Graham, to
OL,18,Ftake over the farm, claiming that he
OL,19,Fwould "have to sell" if hit with a tax
OL,20,Fbill.
