OL,3,CShadow minister meets farmers to
OL,4,Cdiscuss industry issues
OL,6,FMrs Bell added: "You always assume it
OL,7,Fwill just pass on. It's not just
OL,8,Ffarming, it's also those businesses
OL,9,Fallied to farming that are suffering
OL,10,Fbadly."
OL,12,FOther farmers also attended the
OL,13,Fmeeting, what they called an
OL,14,F'emergency summit'.
OL,16,FAndrew McCornick, a Dumfries beef and
OL,17,Fsheep farmer, said: "Our industry is
OL,18,Fgoing to suffer badly. A lot of
OL,19,Fpeople, especially the older
OL,20,Fgeneration, will not have time to get
OL,21,Ftheir estates in order.
