OL,3,CShadow minister meets farmers to
OL,4,Cdiscuss industry issues
OL,6,F"We thought we had ours in order, and
OL,7,Fwe're spending a lot of money
OL,8,Fcorrecting it. All of that, and trying
OL,9,Fto make a living from farming, is
OL,10,Fbecoming very very challenging."
OL,12,FIn the latest budget of two weeks ago,
OL,13,Fthe Chancellor announced a tweak to
OL,14,Fthe policy which would allow spouses
OL,15,Fto transfer any of their unused
OL,16,Finheritance-tax-free allowance.
OL,18,FOn this change, Robbie Moore MP said:
OL,19,F"That just does not go anywhere near
OL,20,Ffar enough.
