OL,6,F"The average size of a farm is about
OL,7,F200 acres, and when you value the farm
OL,8,Fland, a farm house, there might be a
OL,9,Fcottage or two, the crops, the stocks
OL,10,Fin store, the machinery, the
OL,11,Flivestock, you are going to be well
OL,12,Fover that #1million threshold."
OL,14,FIn response to these concerns, a
OL,15,FDepartment for Environment Food and
OL,16,FRural Affairs spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"We're backing farmers with a record
OL,18,F#2.7 billion a year to grow their
OL,19,Fbusinesses and put more British food
OL,20,Fon our plates.
